&#9;The SGWidget module provides access to the @SG_ML_L018015SGWidget ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/sgwidget system and allows you to build graphical user interfaces (GUIs). This is needed for all non command line applications.
&#9;The SGWidget module uses Qt Quick internally to render, so all rendering is GPU accelerated and works on all GPUs. However, everything Qt is abstracted away, so you would never need to touch signal-slot, QML, or JavaScript. Note that @SG_ML_L018015SGWidget ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/sgwidget is a imperative, not declarative, GUI toolkit, making it more familiar to C++ developers. @SG_ML_L021015callback function ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/callback is used instead of signal-slot for event listening and callback functions.
&#9;@SG_ML_L018015SGWidget ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/sgwidget has resizing builtin, so anything using it will resize automatically to fit the screen aspect ratio. This is done using @SG_ML_L01A016w-distance ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/wdistance.
&#9;@SG_ML_L01C018theme colour ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/themecolour is also builtin and user customisable. You are allowed a set of 9 theme colours to build your application with, preferably they should be in a gradient. Note that every year around National Day, the theme of all SGEXTN applications will be switched to For Our Nation, the special National Day theme.
&#9;@SG_ML_L020014application icon ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/appicon is used to display icons on buttons. Note that instead of SVGs or images, fonts are used. This means that the colour of icons always match the theme automatically. Using fonts also provide a performance improvement.
&#9;This module does not have builtin support for displaying images. For images, you need to build a custom shader, which is actually really easily done with @SG_ML_L017015SG - RI ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/renderer.
&#9;@SG_ML_L01B018SingCorrect ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/singcorrect is builtin to all @SG_ML_L018015SGWidget ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/sgwidget input fields. This replaces @SG_ML_L01B018SingCorrect ⁽㈳㈴㈳㈮㈱㈨㈠㈫ ㈧㈤㈱㈤⁾../tutorials/singcorrect commands, which look like LaTeX, with the corresponding Unicode character automatically, making it very easy for the user to input mathematical or scientific notation.
&#9;File uploading and file downloading functionality is provided through @SG_ML_L01101DSGXFileDownloader../cppclass/sgxfiledownloader and @SG_ML_L00F01BSGXFileUploader../cppclass/sgxfileuploader. This refers to bringing files into and out of the application folder, not actually transmitting them over a network.
